prisma generate         Generates Prisma Client from your schema
prisma validate         Validates your schema.prisma file
prisma format           Formats your schema.prisma file

Database

prisma db pull          Introspects DB → pulls schema from existing database
prisma db push          Pushes schema to DB without migration files (good for prototyping)
prisma db seed          Runs your seed script
prisma db execute       Executes raw SQL against your DB

Migrations
prisma migrate dev      Creates + applies migration (development)
prisma migrate deploy   Applies pending migrations (production)
prisma migrate reset    Drops DB, re-applies all migrations + seed
prisma migrate status   Shows which migrations are applied/pending
prisma migrate diff     Diffs two schema states
prisma migrate resolve  Marks a failed migration as resolved

Introspection
prisma introspect       Same as db pull, older alias

Studio
prisma studio           Opens a GUI to browse/edit your database in browser